**LogPulseOrbiter**  
**Description:**  
Transforms log events into orbit-style visualizations to show relationships between systems and error clusters.

```markdown
# LogPulseOrbiter â€“ Orbit-Based Log Mapper

LogPulseOrbiter places log sources as central nodes and shows surrounding error clouds in orbit based on frequency and severity.

## Features
- Circular orbit rendering
- Color-coded severity trails
- Zoom & filter panel

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LogPulseOrbiter.git
cd LogPulseOrbiter
python orbit.py
